robosky.structurehelpers.structure.processor

Class PartialBlockState

  • java.lang.Object
    • robosky.structurehelpers.structure.processor.PartialBlockState

  • public final class PartialBlockState
extends Object
    A representation of a set of BlockState matching a Block and Property values. This is used to determine input and output block states for WeightedChanceProcessor.
    See Also:
    WeightedChanceProcessor, PartialBlockState.Builder
